No. 16,

Original.

Arizona v. California et al. James B. Schnake, Richard J. Daniels, Max O. Truitt, Jr. and Joseph E. Smith for plaintiff. Jack Maxwell Howard, Holloway Jones and Emerson W. Rhyner for the State of California; and George H. Hauerken for Charles L. Harney, Inc., defendants.

The motion for leave to file a bill of complaint is denied. Massachusetts v. Missouri, 308 U. S. 1.
